snippet.title: Resident Evil 4 Professional Mode Gameplay PS2 1080p
snippet.description: Also known as "Baha plays a game for the first time in 5 years and does surprisingly well with it!". I love this game to death, and at some point in the future I actually intend to make a video as to why that is. Another "Why I Love -x-" video most likely.
